---
title: Roasted Eggplant Linguine with Sun-Dried Tomatoes
description: Some days you want to be adventurous and others you just want a little more time to put your feet up. Sun-dried tomatoes are a great secret to adding sweet and concentrated tomato flavours to your dish.
